# Godot Collaboration Rules

This repository uses Godot 4.7.x Standard with GDScript only.

- Do not use lambda functions unless they are clearly necessary.
- Prefer GDScript. Do not add C#/.NET files without explicit team agreement.
- Check `git status` before editing.
- Avoid broad scene or project settings rewrites.
- Only one person should edit the same `*.tscn`, `project.godot`, or Input Map area at a time.
- Do not commit generated `.godot/`, `exports/`, or `builds/` contents.
- Commit Godot `*.import` files together with their source assets.
- Use `cursor/<task>` branches for Cursor/Claude work and open PRs into `main`.
